  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Cases with rhegmatogenous retinal detachment complicated by PVR grade C

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  History of pars plana vitrectomy for PVR grade C

          -  History of silicone oil injection

          -  History of ocular trauma

          -  Diabetic retinopathy

          -  Glaucoma

          -  Giant retinal tear
      </textblock>
